thread.title: Ashley James
thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Ashley James

author: Ashley James
title: Ashley James
text: My dress was beautiful and exactly what I needed for my pageant. Before I bought my dress from here, I ordered from another location and when the dress came it WAS NOT the dress that was in the picture I saw. Peaches Boutique did not let me down and I was so impressed and excited when I actually had the dress in person. The people were patient with me and very helpful especially since I don't live in the area where Peaches Boutique is at.
